    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Beginning at 2nd level, you gain access to Caryll Runes.</p><p> These runes have been passed down from generations of Lunar Slayers, and are believed to be utterings from beings from far beyond that when inspired bear fruit to new power.</p><p> You gain 1 Caryll Rune, and gain additional runes as indicated on the Lunar Slayer class table.</p><p> Caryll Runes are listed at the end of this class, and you can switch any number of Caryll Runes on a long rest.</p><p></p>",
